data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning two-story property, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, awaits your visit. Conveniently located with easy access to Loop 410 and I-35, this residence also boasts proximity to Palo Alto Park, offering a perfect blend of urban convenience and natural beauty. Immerse yourself in the vibrant lifestyle of San Antonio with top-notch restaurants, shopping, and entertainment, all within minutes of this charming abode.    Upon entering, you'll immediately sense the warm and inviting atmosphere that this house exudes. With spacious interiors designed for both entertaining guests and creating a cozy family ambiance, this property strikes the perfect balance between style and comfort
